“IELTS Writing band 9“ is a perfect tool for you to prepare your IELTS Writing test. The aim of this App is to provide band 9 essays about the IELTS Writing, and also to help you improve your English language skills. Especially if you are very busy and have little opportunity to set aside enough time and sit down for practice because writing is very time consuming. With “IELTS Writing band 9 “, now you can prepare IELTS Writing anytime anywhere on the go, it makes your every minute count. 

All these essays are written by Simon Corcoran (an ex-IELTS examiner and I now run IELTS exam preparation courses in Manchester). He is familiar with the main problems students face when preparing to take the writing module. This part, with frequently-tested questions and band 9 model answers written by Simon himself, will expose to you the testing pattern and how to reach the level of the model answers.


Features:
- Simple interface, easy to use;
- 69 Academic writing tasks in real IELTS Writing tests;
- Various types of questions of the IELTS Writing Test; 
- 44 task1 samples (table, bar chart, pie chart, line chart, process diagram, map, design drawing, etc.)
- 29 task2 samples (education, environment, technology, culture, media, etc.)

Let IELTS Writing Essay Pro help you pass the exam by the most excellently!
